== Software not building with Libav ==

Some software might not be compatible with the 0.8 or even the 0.7 Libav API.

The most outstanding issues include:

* libavutil specific function being used without including the required header:
: <code>include <libavutil/mathematics.h></code> to include <code>av_rescale_q()</code>
: <code>include <libavutil/avstring.h></code> to include the <code>av_str</code> functions
* FFmpeg only calls used:
: <code>avformat_alloc_output_context2()</code> might be the most used, it is a shortcut for calling <code>avformat_alloc_context()</code> followed by using <code>av_guess_format()</code> and an <code>av_strlcpy</code> of the filename.

