== Usage ==

Libav provides a new command-line tool to manipulate streams called {{c|avconv}}. Its aim is similar to the {{c|ffmpeg}} command from FFmpeg, but the syntax had been changed to be more regular and it aims to solve some long standing issues regarding time stamp guessing/generation that had been a bane for everybody trying to transcode live streams in the past.

